On june 3, 2015
[281455]

Hello guys!

There is a new ladder for active armies that will be restarted each season! It should be pretty similar to [Ladder] Continious Championship (9) with several additional rules

Rules

0. You can add/use your own armies only!

1. Don't break the forum rules and rules below!

2. Everyone is able to take part in. Make sure (by checking listed armies power) that your army is suitable to join.

3. If you are new you start at the bottom

4. If the link to your army is too long, then you shall use http://tinyurl.com/ service. Eg

wrong : http://kingdom-of-korea.minitroopers....

correct : http://tinyurl.com/KOFKOREA

5. You shall post FULL ARMY NAME and the POWER right after the link to your army (link and full army namve are not always equal!). DON'T forget to update the POWER. Eg

"1. http://tinyurl.com/KOFKOREA KINGDOM OF KOREA / 263"

6. To advance you must beat the army above you, post the replay and change your position in the list

7. If there is a double post please edit the most recent post to have the most up to date list (or post an up to date list).

8. If you have more than one army in the list you shall beat your own army that's above (according to clause 3) to move your second army further.

9. If you know that you won't be able to take part with any army, you shall mark that army with SKIP text. Eg

"3. SKIP http://tinyurl.com/WECOME WECOMEINPIECES / 257"
or
"3. http://tinyurl.com/WECOME WECOMEINPIECES / 257 SKIP"
or
"3. SKIP http://tinyurl.com/WECOME WECOMEINPIECES / 257 SKIP"

10. You can't mark your army with SKIP just for "a second". Armies of abusers will be removed from the list and may be banned until the next season

11. Once per 2-4 weeks I'll check armies that "got stuck". If those armies doesn't attack armies above or attack+beat them without posting a result then "stucked" armies will be marked with SKIP by myself.

- - - - - - -

I'm (KOFKOREA) an administrator of this ladder. If you wanna help with administration, please, contact to me first somehow

On june 3, 2015

[8640217]

My sabotaur has a very special unique ability. Its called "Marksmans Willpower". This ability is so special it cannot be found in my sabotaurs skill sheet nor can it be found on the minitroopers wikia because its my sabotaurs special unique ability.

The way that marksmans willpower works is that when my sabotaur takes damage and reaches really low health and is about to die but does not die, he has a small chance to aquire a boost of energy and strength and this alots him to score multiple kills very quickly.
However, this ability can happen only by chance and may or may not trigger, and often it does NOT trigger. Though if it DOES trigger, it allows my sabotaur to make a comeback and kill like 2-4 enemies really quickly.
During this battle the enemy was tearing my troopers to pieces but my pilot named Gilead used the right grenade (clown grenade) at the right spot (behind the pilot named crusher) and at the right time (when the gametimer reached 1009) then my sabotaur unleashed marksmans willpower and quickly scored a kill, then a double kill, then a triple kill!

[8640217]

Spiral Team vs a new start
My new trooper reached level 5. I had to choose between the coffee that boosts your speed by 25%, and the Famas assault rifle.
I really wanted that coffee since it would work well with On Point, but I figured the Famas would be better.
His weapons often get sabotaged by sabotaurs, and it never hurts to have an backup weapon incase your main weapon gets sabotaged or runs out of ammo. Plus the Famas would work well with his compensator and his Battle Ready ability.

I am hoping for either Comms, Spy, or Munitions when he reach level 6.
